like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ex差唔多半年無覆過我<br />\n勁唔勁<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要人係台灣 我係香港<br />\n\b已經慣左單機<br />\n其實佢都覆過一句 叫我唔洗等<br />\n但過左一個月我又照send野<br />\n<br />\n其實真係好難做番朋友 <br />\n可能佢都唔知點面對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前排都喺自己係到單機緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實講完分手真喺唔知點面對"},{"pid":"1c843b1e32614e880433422f5d5cabdaf2b64cb1","tid":261083,"uid":68589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ex差唔多半年無覆過我<br />\n勁唔勁<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要人係台灣 我係香港<br />\n\b已經慣左單機<br />\n其實佢都覆過一句 叫我唔洗等<br />\n但過左一個月我又照send野<br />\n<br />\n其實真係好難做番朋友 <br />\n可能佢都唔知點面對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前排都喺自己係到單機緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實講完分手真喺唔知點面對</blockquote><br />\n我宜家都係用一種諗法說服緊自己<br />\n人生有好多個三年五年..etc<br />\n每個人都係陪你一段路 以唔同方式幫你成長<br />\n任何一段感情都有終結既時侯 <br />\n但係唔好浪費佢<br />\n珍惜呢段感情帶比你既野<br />\n<br />\n又或者真係有一日有緣份一齊番都唔定<br />\n但呢一刻都唔再重要<br />\n你要focus番係自己到<br />\n因為當你有一日真係遇到更好既人 你唔應該再犯同樣既錯 而係好好咁對佢"},{"pid":"cb2874028d9d3bf969f630a9637b503915cfd46a","tid":261083,"uid":71960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:22:57.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c676ccd2d0566ec0a81ac19f8402a596c3160a","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ex差唔多半年無覆過我<br />\n勁唔勁<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要人係台灣 我係香港<br />\n\b已經慣左單機<br />\n其實佢都覆過一句 叫我唔洗等<br />\n但過左一個月我又照send野<br />\n<br />\n其實真係好難做番朋友 <br />\n可能佢都唔知點面對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前排都喺自己係到單機緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實講完分手真喺唔知點面對</blockquote><br />\n我宜家都係用一種諗法說服緊自己<br />\n人生有好多個三年五年..etc<br />\n每個人都係陪你一段路 以唔同方式幫你成長<br />\n任何一段感情都有終結既時侯 <br />\n但係唔好浪費佢<br />\n珍惜呢段感情帶比你既野<br />\n<br />\n又或者真係有一日有緣份一齊番都唔定<br />\n但呢一刻都唔再重要<br />\n你要focus番係自己到<br />\n因為當你有一日真係遇到更好既人 你唔應該再犯同樣既錯 而係好好咁對佢</blockquote><br />\n講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個人都會教識我地一啲嘢"},{"pid":"5999c77fd86d5e5ce209759be7302e67fcf7e80e","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9f83516e5c72c47a05c14834c06dc20e470d98","tid":261083,"uid":36720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算搵翻佢都唔知講咩好<br />\n不如忘記佢好過啦<br />\n就算佢搵翻我做朋友我都唔會想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ef35bc411366d53e67f4cb7593bf7b109071d7","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算搵翻佢都唔知講咩好<br />\n不如忘記佢好過啦<br />\n就算佢搵翻我做朋友我都唔會想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得做我會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩得知佢入左醫院，諗住問下佢朋友佢咩事，點知佢朋友叫我等陣我等左一個鐘，再睇番佢朋友ig，發現佢叫佢朋友block左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee611db6914a711c1e504e02a18ffb1f9d2b17b1","tid":261083,"uid":6116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"愈愛愈做唔番朋友 <br />\n唔想再傷人"},{"pid":"66ddd483a9343e0f30a3d0591e3fee2c53bcfef5","tid":261083,"uid":93964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T14:35:04.000Z","msg":"扮開心 因為佢有絕症"},{"pid":"17807f5a421aa223e17b7a5e1de743fce3520f22","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愈愛愈做唔番朋友 <br />\n唔想再傷人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為了解而分開<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6db0146bf06dd3eae1470aa8e2d935ef6b6a28","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮開心 因為佢有絕症</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔會嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢有打開波身體好健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5a2d4cfbe5be4aeb79cdf98f27369e2bf9477a","tid":261083,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:19:21.000Z","msg":"關我咩事"},{"pid":"6a9553eb82453d2400e213a7ef5d97ef396c457e","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關我咩事</blockquote><br />\n無人逼你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b754a33808ddd81d40dad28a93d90fca3c5b276c","tid":261083,"uid":36720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T16:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算搵翻佢都唔知講咩好<br />\n不如忘記佢好過啦<br />\n就算佢搵翻我做朋友我都唔會想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得做我會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩得知佢入左醫院，諗住問下佢朋友佢咩事，點知佢朋友叫我等陣我等左一個鐘，再睇番佢朋友ig，發現佢叫佢朋友block左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真係咁缺朋友咩？<br />\n我成日咁問自己<br />\n過客黎姐 忘記佢啦"},{"pid":"ba1d93c87f51d2e5a314067369a8cea60d8c6fa4","tid":261083,"uid":98805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"我ex都有諗住分手想做番朋友 （佢提出分手做朋友）話咩無哂感覺覺得我做朋友好啲 <br />\n我就話如果真係唔俾機會我就寧願block左我 求左佢好多次 最終block左我 因為我過唔到自己個關 雖然頭幾日仲會叫朋友幫我留意佢啲野 但係過一排就同自己講一定要放低佢 下個會更好等等既野 縱使而家有時都會懷緬過去 但係無開始個時咁痛 而家純粹只係當作一個開心既回憶就算<br />\n利申 同ex4年  勸你唔好諗咁多 最好朋友都唔好做啦   <br />\n只會攞苦來辛"},{"pid":"9a1901022a5d6d6d0668378a22380ae5513d61a2","tid":261083,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"我block曬前男友，無顯示電話<br />\n仆街 前幾個月鍾用太空卡打黎想做朋友<br />\n我即刻改電話號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你呢d無尊重人地選擇的人真係好煩"},{"pid":"c6aeca4862d411aee8f084b37e98e2a671b1c33b","tid":261083,"uid":119181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有愛過先做唔返啊<br />\n冇愛過多數好似我咁會想做個朋友就算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我喺想由朋友再慢慢一步步嚟，而唔喺無愛過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣..但身邊既人個個都叫我放手..我卻好固執想由朋友再開始令佢見到我有改變從而番番尼..<br />\n同佢唔會有common fd所以散左就真係冇機會接觸<br />\n只怕用'朋友'身分接近番但最後佢真係fd zone左我咁到時更加冇得救..<br />\n明知依刻佢做d咩都控制唔到但就好想佢番番尼..<br />\n真係好痛好痛 sorry for 1999.."},{"pid":"9efe75a9d4a3954877aa967cc413198cea426552","tid":261083,"uid":119181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>完了吧 如無意外</blockquote><br />\n我只喺想佢番嚟我身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無架喇<br />\n有得say goodbye應該已經算好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解連比我睇住佢生活點滴嘅野都要block埋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經係互不接觸既平行線了</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n好唔甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話分手就分手，話block就block，從此以後變咗最熟悉的陌生人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但曾經卻係最最最親密既一個..突然咩都冇曬..<br />\n比'朋友'更加疏..失去先發現自己原來真係好愛好愛"},{"pid":"4cd789ea50fc30d9f9cb9ac7f45ed571518189cf","tid":261083,"uid":119181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ex差唔多半年無覆過我<br />\n勁唔勁<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要人係台灣 我係香港<br />\n\b已經慣左單機<br />\n其實佢都覆過一句 叫我唔洗等<br />\n但過左一個月我又照send野<br />\n<br />\n其實真係好難做番朋友 <br />\n可能佢都唔知點面對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前排都喺自己係到單機緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實講完分手真喺唔知點面對</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n初戀..上個月月尾佢講分手..本身前日就一年..<br />\n崩潰左成個月 期間仲大病埋而家身體仲未好反曬.."},{"pid":"2050c25ab38d5e435844b0cc6ab7e93955ac6c97","tid":261083,"uid":76592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:40:24.000Z","msg":"絕d係對你好<br />\n真係賤人宜家係會收你做兵"},{"pid":"8c19bd2834a8a90e22c63ea16aafc4bf640a9734","tid":261083,"uid":59863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:44:24.000Z","msg":"過來人經驗  做朋友真會令自已難受"},{"pid":"f4eee0cd138f00935cbfbb7e425ccc97391a38d8","tid":261083,"uid":76592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T17:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過來人經驗  做朋友真會令自已難受</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942973798f9b0faa99405b98216236030b78a97a","tid":261083,"uid":87528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:02:37.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩，點撚解分咗手要做返朋友，做唔返架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658453bfd708e14890886bf4cde44725b0b1330a","tid":261083,"uid":102138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:11:01.000Z","msg":"俾你做到所謂嘅朋友仲痛苦<br />\n佢咁絕對你黎講係好事"},{"pid":"c4ee82e21260e4bd41cba05d5fbf7abe11e238bd","tid":261083,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過來人經驗  做朋友真會令自已難受</blockquote><br />\n我同ex而家都做到朋友<br />\n當年我屋企有事都係靠佢開解我<br />\n分咗手後一年先至和好返<br />\n有時撞到面會傾兩句近況<br />\n但每次佢同我講要好好愛錫女朋友<br />\n我都會好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n久而久之先發覺我只係將佢投射落現任<br />\n但我又唔希望因為現任而失去咗一個曾經幫我走過難關嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fa5288c75b969ed39ce844fe0c7cc51fd92221","tid":261083,"uid":4130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:25:34.000Z","msg":"有得做都唔好做<br />\n我Ex覺得我對佢好好 想同我做返好朋友 <br />\n每日都會搵啲野同我傾下 <br />\n但其實我未完全放得低 <br />\n有次嘈交我直頭要求佢唔好再搵我 佢唔肯<br />\n但佢有中意既人 所以我雖然好想同返佢一齊<br />\n但我知道已經無可能 <br />\n唯有一直hea覆佢咁樣去淡忘佢<br />\n<br />\n做返朋友只會令你一直都放唔低<br />\n做唔返先好"},{"pid":"cc35f722d56a39f26cdbe77c3733ceb0feef0a92","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算搵翻佢都唔知講咩好<br />\n不如忘記佢好過啦<br />\n就算佢搵翻我做朋友我都唔會想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得做我會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩得知佢入左醫院，諗住問下佢朋友佢咩事，點知佢朋友叫我等陣我等左一個鐘，再睇番佢朋友ig，發現佢叫佢朋友block左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真係咁缺朋友咩？<br />\n我成日咁問自己<br />\n過客黎姐 忘記佢啦</blockquote><br />\n我唔缺，你你經歷過你一定明，依個時候朋友講咩都喺廢，你唔會聽得入耳"},{"pid":"48293bbded5128c71c86f8248bd5210f9fe9ba9c","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我ex都有諗住分手想做番朋友 （佢提出分手做朋友）話咩無哂感覺覺得我做朋友好啲 <br />\n我就話如果真係唔俾機會我就寧願block左我 求左佢好多次 最終block左我 因為我過唔到自己個關 雖然頭幾日仲會叫朋友幫我留意佢啲野 但係過一排就同自己講一定要放低佢 下個會更好等等既野 縱使而家有時都會懷緬過去 但係無開始個時咁痛 而家純粹只係當作一個開心既回憶就算<br />\n利申 同ex4年  勸你唔好諗咁多 最好朋友都唔好做啦   <br />\n只會攞苦來辛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢都做到咁絕得仲可點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed050787adca8b2c4d4af1146281c39713ea9f8","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我block曬前男友，無顯示電話<br />\n仆街 前幾個月鍾用太空卡打黎想做朋友<br />\n我即刻改電話號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你呢d無尊重人地選擇的人真係好煩</blockquote><br />\n改埋電話號碼又好似誇張左小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5d9233b742879bd38a523e7fb859182cec31a8","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ex差唔多半年無覆過我<br />\n勁唔勁<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要人係台灣 我係香港<br />\n\b已經慣左單機<br />\n其實佢都覆過一句 叫我唔洗等<br />\n但過左一個月我又照send野<br />\n<br />\n其實真係好難做番朋友 <br />\n可能佢都唔知點面對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前排都喺自己係到單機緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實講完分手真喺唔知點面對</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n初戀..上個月月尾佢講分手..本身前日就一年..<br />\n崩潰左成個月 期間仲大病埋而家身體仲未好反曬..</blockquote><br />\ntake care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75dffa07eabdb4b372790b14e2bbac959caae703","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絕d係對你好<br />\n真係賤人宜家係會收你做兵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568892731048c8976fc1e556b630c5acd53e4c91","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有得做都唔好做<br />\n我Ex覺得我對佢好好 想同我做返好朋友 <br />\n每日都會搵啲野同我傾下 <br />\n但其實我未完全放得低 <br />\n有次嘈交我直頭要求佢唔好再搵我 佢唔肯<br />\n但佢有中意既人 所以我雖然好想同返佢一齊<br />\n但我知道已經無可能 <br />\n唯有一直hea覆佢咁樣去淡忘佢<br />\n<br />\n做返朋友只會令你一直都放唔低<br />\n做唔返先好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我覺得真喺唔洗去到依個地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8e9f694ddd1d54cbaab79d85e64946267a3d8d","tid":261083,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:34:10.000Z","msg":"男人老狗block 人好小家"},{"pid":"a250ff5a5d486fa0c8b16b1bac2ef3c184b12a03","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人老狗block 人好小家</blockquote><br />\n我覺得咁樣好小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6024905dd0d2bb73b273f81450baf85e1c396f31","tid":261083,"uid":58543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:40:06.000Z","msg":"做sp都有d機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3a966abcb963f82dd6754508b7c2cc75b9cf0c","tid":261083,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T00:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>完了吧 如無意外</blockquote><br />\n我只喺想佢番嚟我身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無架喇<br />\n有得say goodbye應該已經算好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解連比我睇住佢生活點滴嘅野都要block埋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經係互不接觸既平行線了</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n好唔甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話分手就分手，話block就block，從此以後變咗最熟悉的陌生人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但曾經卻係最最最親密既一個..突然咩都冇曬..<br />\n比'朋友'更加疏..失去先發現自己原來真係好愛好愛</blockquote><br />\n可能我同佢唔算一齊過所以都唔算分開<br />\n只係變翻陌生人好快就唔記得哂啲嘢"},{"pid":"174ad6312a7e1e159441a6f1a6ab80182f86d0fb","tid":261083,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T00:42:31.000Z","msg":"我明白樓主感受。<br />\n做得返朋友，一係根本無愛過，一係仲有一個仲愛緊。<br />\n我曾經都好傻，人哋講咗唔愛我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲乞求佢話做朋友，每日照Whatsapp傾吓啲日常生活，扮無事，結果佢有日同我講：我哋都係唔好再聯絡。<br />\n嗰次之後，無再搵過佢，其實做朋友只會辛苦咗自己，又放唔低。<br />\n喺地吓攞返起樽鹽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63206484694c721e765848e5a9fbff057fcb1d58","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做sp都有d機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsp都無得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b901c5ef32b012e13df9112a177aab2e75c4f3","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我只喺想佢番嚟我身邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無架喇<br />\n有得say goodbye應該已經算好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解連比我睇住佢生活點滴嘅野都要block埋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經係互不接觸既平行線了</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n好唔甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話分手就分手，話block就block，從此以後變咗最熟悉的陌生人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但曾經卻係最最最親密既一個..突然咩都冇曬..<br />\n比'朋友'更加疏..失去先發現自己原來真係好愛好愛</blockquote><br />\n可能我同佢唔算一齊過所以都唔算分開<br />\n只係變翻陌生人好快就唔記得哂啲嘢</blockquote><br />\n咁喺未深愛過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c10bdba57c474bd05d15543c1815ca0b2d17423","tid":261083,"uid":9524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明白樓主感受。<br />\n做得返朋友，一係根本無愛過，一係仲有一個仲愛緊。<br />\n我曾經都好傻，人哋講咗唔愛我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲乞求佢話做朋友，每日照Whatsapp傾吓啲日常生活，扮無事，結果佢有日同我講：我哋都係唔好再聯絡。<br />\n嗰次之後，無再搵過佢，其實做朋友只會辛苦咗自己，又放唔低。<br />\n喺地吓攞返起樽鹽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我只喺覺得仲有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢只喺講左句我會慢慢block曬你所有嘢，結果兩日佢就block曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22a156d32d5474b227c4000c58313f1ad7cfdd2","tid":261083,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n無架喇<br />\n有得say goodbye應該已經算好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解連比我睇住佢生活點滴嘅野都要block埋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經係互不接觸既平行線了</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n好唔甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話分手就分手，話block就block，從此以後變咗最熟悉的陌生人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但曾經卻係最最最親密既一個..突然咩都冇曬..<br />\n比'朋友'更加疏..失去先發現自己原來真係好愛好愛</blockquote><br />\n可能我同佢唔算一齊過所以都唔算分開<br />\n只係變翻陌生人好快就唔記得哂啲嘢</blockquote><br />\n咁喺未深愛過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對我嚟講未嘗唔係一件好事"},{"pid":"b59